├15
├├151
├└152
└16"""  -- FIXME: `├├└1421` is not beautiful at all


      it "`toString`: Triangles" $ do

        (Convert.toString Convert.Triangles show $ 1 :<
            [ ql 11
            , 12 :<~ [ 121, 122, 123 ]
            , 13 :<~ [ 131 ]
            , 14 :< [ ql 141, 142 :<~ [ 1421 ] ]
            , 15 :<~ [ 151, 152 ]
            , ql 16
            ])
        `shouldEqual` """1
